= Game Mechanics =

This page documents the game mechanics of Mappy-Land for the NES.

== Overview ==

Mappy-Land is a platformer featuring Mappy the police mouse collecting gifts for his girlfriend Mapico. Unlike the original Mappy arcade game, this features side-scrolling levels with various themes.

