== Lives and Game Over ==

=== Starting Lives ===

* Default: 3 lives
* Extra life at: 20,000 points
* Continue: From current world start

=== Losing a Life ===

Mappy loses a life when:
* Touched by a cat
* Time runs out
* Falls off screen
* Hit by obstacle

