== Tips and Strategies ==

=== Collecting Efficiently ===

* Plan routes to minimize backtracking
* Use trampolines to reach high platforms
* Time jumps to avoid cats
* Collect fish to distract cats

=== Dealing with Cats ===

* Baseballs stun cats temporarily
* Fish makes cats chase the fish instead
* Trampolines can be used to jump over cats
* Doors provide brief safety

=== Time Management ===

* Each level has a time limit
* Remaining time converts to points
* Don't rush - plan your route
* Some items extend time

